94 Sanidassanattika, Sauttaraduka
Sanidassanattika, Sauttaraduka
145.
344Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ sauttaraṃ dhammaṃ paccayā nasanidassanasappaṭigho nasauttaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
345Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ anuttaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho naanuttaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha…pe…  avigate cha.
